wiki_tab.content:
[Verse 1]
[tab][ch]D[/ch]                         [ch]Bm[/ch]
Hey there drama, are you into karma?[/tab]
[tab] [ch]F#m[/ch]                             [ch]A[/ch]
Cause I'm dying to believe you're next[/tab]
[tab]           [ch]D[/ch]
Oh is your mind erasing?[/tab]
[tab]              [ch]Bm[/ch]
Well then you better chase it[/tab]
[tab]          [ch]F#m[/ch]                       [ch]A[/ch]
Cause the thought it scaring me to death[/tab]
[tab]        [ch]D[/ch]
Can you feel it?[/tab]
[tab]        [ch]Bm[/ch]
Cause I feel it now[/tab]
[tab]        [ch]F#m[/ch]
Are you shaking?[/tab]

[Pre-Chorus]
[tab]       [ch]A[/ch]                         [ch]D[/ch]
Do you know that it's never ever gonna be the way you want it?[/tab]
[tab][ch]Bm[/ch]                      [ch]F#m[/ch]
So come on get your fix now, now, now[/tab]
[tab][ch]A[/ch]
You drive me crazy with that[/tab]

[Chorus]
[tab][ch]D[/ch]          [ch]Bm[/ch]                  [ch]F#m[/ch]                [ch]A[/ch]                 [ch]D[/ch]            [ch]Bm[/ch]
Chit chat, do you want that or wanna take me home tonight? All this chit chat is holding me back.[/tab]
[tab][ch]F#m[/ch]                            [ch]A[/ch]      [ch]D[/ch]                      [ch]Bm[/ch]
I'm breaking just to bend your light. I thought I told you I really need your sugar[/tab]
[tab][ch]F#m[/ch]               [ch]A[/ch]
A roller coaster, I'm going supernova[/tab]
[tab][ch]D[/ch]                 [ch]Bm[/ch]                   [ch]F#m[/ch]  [ch]A[/ch]
This chit chat is holding me back from you, you[/tab]

[tab][ch]D[/ch]                     [ch]Bm[/ch]
